{"pageProps":{"post":{"title":"예쁘게 꾸미자 Sass - 문법편","date":"2023-06-05","slug":"2023-06-04-Sass-2","content":"<h1>✨ 기본 작성법</h1>\n<h2>1. 중첩</h2>\n<p>Sass의 가장 큰 자랑, 장점 바로 <span class=\"point\">중첩</span>입니다.<br>\n기존 우리가 CSS를 작성할 때에는 부모에서 자식순으로 선택자를 선택하여 적용하게 되는데,<br>\n이는 상위선택자를 반복적으로 사용하기 때문에 불편함이 발생합니다.</p>\n<p>하지만 Scss에서는 중첩이 가능하기 때문에 부모 선택자는 한번 선언 후 그 안에 자식 선택자들을 선언할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"flex_box\">\r\n<div class=\"flex_item\">\n<h6>scss</h6>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.parents</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  width: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">300</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.children1</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    width: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">200</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.children2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    width: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">300</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"flex_item\">\n<h6>css</h6>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"css\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"css\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.parents</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{width: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">300</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.parents</span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.children1</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{width: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">200</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.parents</span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.children2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{width: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">300</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\r\n</div>\n<p>단순합니다.😄<br>\n이는 반복적인 선택자를 사용할 필요없고 누구의 부모인지, 자식인지 한 눈에 들어오기 때문에 개발시에도 매우 유용합니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2>2. 부모 선택자 <code>$</code></h2>\n<p>scss에서는 위와 같이 중첩이 사용됩니다. 만약 이 때 <strong>부모 선택자를 선택</strong>하고 싶다면 <code>$</code>를 사용하면 됩니다.<br>\n<code>&#x26;</code>를 사용하면 부모 선택자를 굳이 반복할 필요 없이 바로 선언 가능합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"flex_box\">\r\n<div class=\"flex_item\">\n<h6>scss</h6>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.parents</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">black</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">&#x26;</span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">:hover</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">red</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">&#x26;</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">_01</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">blue</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.red</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> + </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">&#x26;</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">green</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"flex_item\">\n<h6>css</h6>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"css\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"css\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.parents</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">black</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.parents</span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">:hover</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">red</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.parents_01</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">blue</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.red</span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">+</span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.parents</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> {background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">green</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"alert\">\n<h6><code>&#x26;</code>은 선택자의 시작 부분에서만 사용가능합니다.</h6>\n<p>예를 들어 <code>span&#x26;</code> 같이 특정 엘리먼트 뒤에서는 사용 불가능합니다.</p>\n</div>\n<br>\n<h2>3. 변수</h2>\n<p>Sass에서는 <code>$변수명: 값</code> 형식을 통해 변수 선언이 가능합니다.<br>\n주로 color, font style 등을 선언하여 다양하게 사용합니다.</p>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$white</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">#fff</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$font-fmaily</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">'Inter'</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">'Noto Sans KR'</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">sans-serif</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>또한 전역 변수로도 사용할 수 있지만, 변수의 선언 위치에 따라 지역변수로도 사용 가능합니다.</p>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"css\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"css\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.wrap</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  $bgColor: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">black</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  .container{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    background: $bgColor; // black</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.header</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  $bgColor: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">red</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  &#x26;_inner{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    background: $bgColor; // red</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"alert\">\n<h6>CSS 변수와 SCSS 변수의 차이점</h6>\n<ul>\n<li>Scss 변수는 컴파일 되면서 CSS 파일에서는 모두 사라짐</li>\n<li>Scss 변수는 재할당 되어도 이전 내용이 변하지 않지만 CSS는 재할당시 이전내용도 모두 같이 변경</li>\n<li>Scss의 변수명에서 <code>_</code>와 <code>-</code>은 구분하지 않음</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<br>\n<h2>보간</h2>\n<p>선택자나, 속성, 문자열에는 바로 사용이 불가능합니다.<br>\n이를 처리하기 위하여 문자 보간 (<code>#{}</code>)이라는 걸 사용하게 되는데, 아래 예시를 참고해주세요!</p>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$name</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: point;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$color</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">blue</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$border</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">border</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$size</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">200</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.test</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">#{$name}</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    background: </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">url</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">'/point/</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">#{$color}</span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">.svg'</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">#{$border}</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">solid</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">blue</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    width: </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">calc</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">100</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">%</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">-</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">#{</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">size</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">}</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">*</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">))</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>참고로 보간의 리턴값은 단순 문자열(string)입니다.<br>\n단위 사이에 끼워 넣는 경우 오류가 발생해도 그대로 출력하기 때문에 에러를 잡을 수 없어 단위를 곱하는 방식으로 사용하시길 바랍니다.</p>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$size</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">100</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">/* Bad 👎 */</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.test1</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  width: </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">#{$size}</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">px;  </span><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">/* 100pxpx */</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">/* Good 👍*/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.test1</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  width: </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">#{$size}</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">*</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">; </span><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">/* error */</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2>Mixins</h2>\n<p>Mixin은 재사용할 CSS 스타일을 정의하는 기능입니다.<br>\nreact에서는 컴포넌트와 비슷한 기능이죠~</p>\n<p>먼저 <code>@mixin</code>을 사용해 스타일을 정의하고 <code>@include</code>를 통해서 가져옵니다.</p>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">@mixin</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">bg-color</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">black</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  color: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">white</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.btn</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">@include</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">bg-color</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>변수와 같이 사용하여 아래와 같이 응용할 수 있습니다!</p>\n<div class=\"flex_box\">\r\n<div class=\"flex_item\">\n<h6>scss</h6>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">@mixin</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">position</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$type</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$left</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">5</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$top</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">){</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  position: </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$type</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  left: </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$left</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">top</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$top</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.box</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">@include</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">position</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">absolute</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">15</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">5</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">); </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.box1</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">@include</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">position</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">absolute</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">$top</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">15</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">); </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"flex_item\">\n<h6>css</h6>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"css\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"css\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.box</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  position: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">absolute</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  left: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">15</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  top: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">5</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.box1</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  position: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">absolute</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  left: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">5</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  top: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">5</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">px</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\n<h2>Extend</h2>\n<p>extend는 말그대로 확장입니다.<br>\n원래 속성에 더 확장하여 스타일을 선언한다고 생각하시면 될 것 같습니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h1>✨ Reference</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://smartstudio.tech/node-sass-to-dart-sass/\">https://smartstudio.tech/node-sass-to-dart-sass/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://smartstudio.tech/node-sass-to-dart-sass/\">https://smartstudio.tech/node-sass-to-dart-sass/</a></li>\n</ul>","coverImage":"/assets/blog/cover/sass.jpg"}},"__N_SSG":true}